questions.question:
What is the output of the following code?

```php
$x = 10;
$y = 20;
echo $x + $y;
```

What is the output of the following code?

```php
$x = '10';
$y = 20;
echo $x + $y;
```

What is the output of the following code?

```php
$x = 5;
echo ++$x;
```

What is the output of the following code?

```php
$x = 5;
echo $x++;
```

What is the output of the following code?

```php
$x = 10;
$y = '10';
if ($x == $y) {
    echo 'Equal';
} else {
    echo 'Not Equal';
}
```

What is the output of the following code?

```php
$x = 10;
$y = '10';
if ($x === $y) {
    echo 'Equal';
} else {
    echo 'Not Equal';
}
```
